OL,3,CIt's a 'no-brainer': Prison officers
OL,4,Ccall for stab vests in dangerous jails
OL,6,FPrison officers have urged Justice
OL,7,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood to give them
OL,8,Fmore protective gear following an
OL,9,Fattack on several guards at a County
OL,10,FDurham jail.
OL,12,FFour prison officers were injured at
OL,13,FHMP Frankland by Manchester Arena bomb
OL,14,Fplotter Hashem Abedi, with three taken
OL,15,Fto hospital earlier this month.
OL,17,FThey were attacked with hot oil and
OL,18,Fhomemade weapons,
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
