OL,3,CIt's a 'no-brainer': Prison officers
OL,4,Ccall for stab vests in dangerous jails
OL,6,F"So we should hope that those stab-
OL,7,Fproof vests would be rolled out after
OL,8,Fthis rapid review."
OL,10,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,11,Fpreviously announced the Prison
OL,12,FService will investigate whether
OL,13,Ffrontline staff should be given
OL,14,Fprotective body armour and the
OL,15,FMinistry of Justice has pledged to
OL,16,Fcarry out a review following the
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,19,FThe Justice Secretary announced
OL,20,Fyesterday (22 April) that the use of
OL,21,Ftasers in prison will be trialed.
