OL,3,CIt's a 'no-brainer': Prison officers
OL,4,Ccall for stab vests in dangerous jails
OL,6,FSpeaking in the House of Commons on
OL,7,FTuesday, Ms Mahmood said: "The House
OL,8,Fwill be aware of the attack at HMP
OL,9,FFrankland on the 12 of April. The
OL,10,Fbravery of the officers involved that
OL,11,Fday undoubtedly saved lives, my
OL,12,Fthoughts are with them as they recover.
OL,14,F"I can today announce that HMPPS (HM
OL,15,FPrison and Probation Service) will
OL,16,Ftrial the use of Tasers in our prisons.
OL,18,F"Wherever we can strengthen our
OL,19,Fdefences, to better protect our staff
OL,20,Fand the public, we will do so."
