OL,3,CIt's a 'no-brainer': Prison officers
OL,4,Ccall for stab vests in dangerous jails
OL,6,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We will do whatever it takes to
OL,8,Fprotect our hardworking staff. Since
OL,9,FNovember last year, the Prison Service
OL,10,Fhas been exploring the use of Tasers
OL,11,Fin our prisons.
OL,13,F"This summer, an operational trial
OL,14,Finto Tasers will be launched for
OL,15,Fspecialised officers to help staff
OL,16,Frespond to high-risk incidents more
OL,17,Feffectively."
